{"type": "article", "id": 14650, "title": "酒瓶灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-09T07:27:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003156Hb5SxmU1laYnNyr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t打碎了的酒瓶怎么办？来自伦敦的设计师 Ryan Jongwoo Choi 设计的酒瓶灯颇有废物利用的意义。将灯泡吊进酒瓶里，下方用一块木板封口，就是一盏很有情调的酒瓶灯了。尽管光线并不明亮，红色的灯丝还是能透过黑色的玻璃瓶而显得格外清楚，尤其适合酒吧等不需要明亮灯光的场所。不过，酒瓶的开口还是精确地计算了角度，防止倾斜的酒瓶再次打碎。<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2015/09/07/go-home-lamp-youre-drunk/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261421142ZJA5Tp7yrXbRnuI.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142115Oi4jybDogxWSTrEw.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142116UZQW7rELdc6BmMuv.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}